name: df-hmeo
params: setvar s0, setvar s1, setvar s2
body: |- wceq(chmeo, cmpo(s0, s1, ctop, ctop, crab(s2, co(cv(s0), ccn, cv(s1)), wcel(ccnv(cv(s2)), co(cv(s1), ccn, cv(s0))))))
bodyPretty: ⊢ Homeo =(s0 ∈ Top, s1 ∈ Top ↦ { s2 ∈(s0[Cn]s1)| `' s2 ∈(s1[Cn]s0)})
comment: Function returning all the homeomorphisms from topology ` j ` to topology ` k ` . (Contributed by FL, 14-Feb-2007.)
